OL,3,CSentencing guidelines for drug
OL,4,Coffences criticised as 'out of date'
OL,6,FCalls are being made to reform
OL,7,FGuernsey's drug sentencing laws, with
OL,8,Fpoliticians, activists and legal
OL,9,Fprofessionals describing them as "out
OL,10,Fof date" and not fit for purpose.
OL,12,FIt comes after a 23-year-old man was
OL,13,Fsentenced to nine and a half years in
OL,14,Fprison for illegally importing 19 bars
OL,15,Fof cannabis chocolate to the island
OL,16,Fearlier this year.
