OL,3,CSentencing guidelines for drug
OL,4,Coffences criticised as 'out of date'
OL,6,FCory Lucas Cabral Le Sauvage's
OL,7,Fsentence was decided according to a
OL,8,Fsystem known as the 'Richards
OL,9,FGuidelines' - a set of principles that
OL,10,Fhave been in place since 2002.
OL,12,FThis provides a framework for
OL,13,Fsentencing drug importation offences
OL,14,Faccording to the class of substance
OL,15,Fimported and its weight.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
