OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1760020384
OL,3,CSentencing guidelines for drug
OL,4,Coffences criticised as 'out of date'
OL,6,FHowever, the guidelines were
OL,7,Finterpreted in a way that meant Le
OL,8,FSauvage's jail time was decided on the
OL,9,Fweight of the overall chocolate bars,
OL,10,Frather than the amount of the
OL,11,Fcontrolled drug within them.
OL,13,FTherefore, his sentence was based on
OL,14,Fthe figure of 768 grams - the weight
OL,15,Fof 19 chocolate bars - rather than the
OL,16,F1.15 grams of THC, the element of
OL,17,Fcannabis, within them.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
