OL,6,FThe Bailiffs of both islands - Sir de
OL,7,FVic Carey and Sir Philip Bailhache -
OL,8,Fwere involved in creating the system,
OL,9,Fat which time Sir de Vic Carey
OL,10,Finstructed that "personal use should
OL,11,Fnot generally result in a lighter
OL,12,Fsentence" as all drugs "add to the
OL,13,Fstock of the island".
