OL,4,Coffences criticised as 'out of date'
OL,6,FHowever, he instructed that the
OL,7,FRichards Guidelines were not an
OL,8,Fattempt to establish "some sort of
OL,9,Finflexible code, which covers all of
OL,10,Fthe issues involved in sentencing for
OL,11,Fsuch offences, some of which must as
OL,12,Fyet be unknown and incapable of
OL,13,Fanticipation".
OL,15,FHe added: "These are general
OL,16,Fguidelines only. Sentencing is always
OL,17,Fa matter for the Court's discretion -
OL,18,Fit is an art and not a science."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
