OL,4,Coffences criticised as 'out of date'
OL,6,FLe Sauvage successfully appealed his
OL,7,Fcase last month, receiving a reduced
OL,8,Fprison term of seven years.
OL,10,FReflecting on Le Sauvage's case,
OL,11,FProfessor Harry Sumnall - a psychology
OL,12,Fprofessor specialising in substance
OL,13,Fuse at Liverpool John Moores
OL,14,FUniversity - says, "in the UK that
OL,15,Fwould probably be very unlikely to
OL,16,Flead to such a high sentence".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
