OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1760020384
OL,3,CSentencing guidelines for drug
OL,4,Coffences criticised as 'out of date'
OL,6,FHe adds: "Indeed, you very rarely
OL,7,Fencounter convictions in relation to
OL,8,FClass A drugs like powder cocaine or
OL,9,Fheroin of a similar type or quantity
OL,10,Fwhich would lead to a similar
OL,11,Fcustodial sentence.
OL,13,F"In the UK, we do have similar systems
OL,14,Fand guidelines in terms of the
OL,15,Fboundaries - they are not too
OL,16,Fdifferent in terms of a minimum and a
OL,17,Fmaximum - but people in the UK are
OL,18,Fmuch less likely to receive a
OL,19,Fcustodial sentence."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
