OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1760020384
OL,3,CSentencing guidelines for drug
OL,4,Coffences criticised as 'out of date'
OL,6,FWhilst 15% of prisoners in the UK are
OL,7,Fin jail for drug offences, in Guernsey
OL,8,Fthe figure is almost 25%.
OL,10,FLegal professionals on the island echo
OL,11,FProfessor Sumnall's beliefs - arguing
OL,12,Fdrug importation sentences on the
OL,13,Fisland are significantly more severe
OL,14,Fthan they would be in the UK.
OL,16,FAdvocate Simon Steel says the Richards
OL,17,FGuidelines must now be considered "out
OL,18,Fof date".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
