OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1760020384
OL,3,CSentencing guidelines for drug
OL,4,Coffences criticised as 'out of date'
OL,6,F"Court time has been used up dealing
OL,7,Fwith substances that do not fit neatly
OL,8,Finto the current guidelines," he
OL,9,Fexplains.
OL,11,F"Ketamine, liquid THC, liquid MDMA,
OL,12,Fsynthetic cannabis - there are plenty
OL,13,Fof examples over recent years."
OL,15,FIn 2020, the States approved a series
OL,16,Fof alternative sentences as part of a
OL,17,Fpiece of work looking to reform the
OL,18,Fisland's justice system.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
