OL,3,CSentencing guidelines for drug
OL,4,Coffences criticised as 'out of date'
OL,6,FThe recommendations included altering
OL,7,Fsentences for drug offences; however,
OL,8,Fmany of these changes have not been
OL,9,Fimplemented.
OL,11,FDeputy Marc Leadbeater, President for
OL,12,Fthe Committee of Home Affairs, says
OL,13,Freform is something his committee is
OL,14,Fnow looking into.
OL,16,F"I can't really speak for the previous
OL,17,Fcommittee and how they nailed down
OL,18,Ftheir priorities and what they wanted
OL,19,Fto progress," he explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
