OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1760020384
OL,3,CSentencing guidelines for drug
OL,4,Coffences criticised as 'out of date'
OL,6,F"You always get hangover from the
OL,7,Fprevious committee, there's always
OL,8,Fpieces of work that are unfinished
OL,9,Fthat the new committee will have to
OL,10,Ftake on board and progress.
OL,12,F"The justice piece of work is
OL,13,Fsomething I am glad my committee can
OL,14,Fhave some involvement in, as it's
OL,15,Fsomething I feel quite strongly about."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/11
